        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the beef is browning, peel and chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Cut your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> in half (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon)</p><p>Chop <strong>half</strong> your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> into bite-sized chunks</p><p>Chop <strong>half </strong>your <strong>tomato[es]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
