    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve the<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>in 475ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [600ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [800ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> ginger & garlic paste</strong>,<strong> tomato paste </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Stir it all together<strong> </strong>–<strong> </strong>this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1670331257411-x200.jpg",
