        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced pepper </strong>and<strong> diced tomato</strong></p><p>Cook for 5-6 min or until softening, then add your <strong>ground turmeric</strong>, a splash of <strong>cold water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Cook for a final 3-4 min – this is your <strong>turmeric pepper chutney</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
